---
title: Warming Venison & Beef Cottage Pie with Extra Cheesy Potato Mash Topping
description: This classic comfort dish is the perfect way to warm up on chilly nights. Imagine a hearty hug on a plate, with a rich, meaty filling topped with a fluffy blanket of cheesy mashed potatoes. Happiness is just a bite away!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604f0010d5f299b40db829f-52e5cb76.jpeg
